description: Previously grazed by sheep, and surrounded by trees, half of the land at the heart of a perplexing criminal investigation is covered by an enormous mound of festering rubbish.
title: Tracked down by the Daily Mail, the man who owns land in Oxfordshire that a stinking river of rubbish has been dumped on. GUY ADAMS exposes exactly how criminal gang operated, eye-watering cost... and the twist NO ONE saw coming

description: Staying Alive icon Finola Hughes bundled up for a laid-back outing in Los Angeles this past week.
title: Staying Alive icon Finola Hughes makes rare public outing… 42 years after starring with John Travolta

description: Where you are today is the accumulation of everything that has happened to you so far in your life. Each one of us has taken a series of paths - either by accident or by choice - to end up where we are.
title: The seven simple steps to manifesting and making your wildest dreams come true: Carolyn is proof it works. Now she reveals everything from finding love to getting rich and how to harness the power of your mind

description: What with the drugs and the bankruptcies and the gruesome surgeries and the toxic relationships (not least with herself), Jenny Johnston asks: how on earth is Kerry Katona still here?
title: I fear for Katie Price. I overdosed twice on cocaine. Now I'm an OnlyFans millionaire, my children go to private school: KERRY KATONA tells everything in the most jaw-dropping interview you'll ever read

description: Instead of shining a light through the fog of digital distortion which blights all our efforts to learn the truth, BBC News has become part of the problem, not the solution, writes ANDREW NEIL.
title: ANDREW NEIL: No amount of arm twisting will stem the tide of licence fee refuseniks - and that's why I believe the BBC's demise is inevitable

description: While Harrison Sullivan's colourful life has been well documented, the Mail can today reveal the troubled young man's father is none other than former England rugby star Victor Ubogu.
title: REVEALED: Humiliated HSTikkyTokky's father is an English rugby legend: Daily Mail investigation exposes astonishing truth about sordid sexual behaviour, money and mum's house lies... and the missing father that explains so much

description: JAN MOIR: Holy jar of sainted jam, I think, driving along Route 101 from Montecito to Summerland in the rosy sunshine of a Californian winter.
title: JAN MOIR: My trip to Meghan Markle's pop up shop where even the Montecito set baulk at £24 for a jar of honey!

description: Shona McGarty found herself caught up in an awkward innuendo with Martin Kemp during Friday night's episode of I'm A Celeb.
title: I'm A Celeb's Shona McGarty left red-faced as she is caught up in awkward innuendo with Martin Kemp during dunny trial

description: Blindfolded drinkers were put to the taste test when handed the same drink to try only in different vessels - with scientists now revealing the results.
title: How the shape of your beer glass can change how your drink tastes

description: It is understood the Prime Minister will announce a decision next month despite warnings over national security. MI5 warn security threat from Chinese spies seeking to infiltrate Parliament.
title: Anger as Sir Keir Starmer to approve Chinese mega-embassy despite MI5 spy warning

description: I'm A Celebrity fans have accused Jack Osbourne of 'rage-baiting' the camp during Friday night's episode.
title: I'm A Celebrity fans accuse Jack Osbourne of 'rage-baiting' the camp amid tense feud with Kelly Brook

description: The actor Qasim Akhtar, 34, who played Zeedan Nazir in the ITV soap, is seen smiling as he is embraced by American cleric Uthman ibn Farooq.
title: Coronation Street star poses beside 'sex slave' speech hate preacher who was banned from the UK

description: This was widely expected to be the 13th and final season for the 36-year-old tight end, who has won three Super Bowls with the Chiefs.  Kelce announced his engagement to Taylor Swift back in August.
title: Travis Kelce speaks out on his retirement plans as NFL legend, 36, enters final months of his Chiefs contract
